				<h5>MEDIA CONTACTS</h5>

				<p>
					Following is a media relations contact list for The Salvation Army in Florida. State media relations are handled by Florida Divisional Headquarters. All local media are asked to first contact their local Salvation Army representative for requests for spokespersons and other inquiries.
				</p>

				<p>
					&nbsp;
				</p>

				<div class="contacts">
					<div class="card" style="width:100% !important;">
						<div class="layer">
							&nbsp;
						</div>

						<div class="content">
							<i class="ministriesGrid-icon icon icon-shield"></i>
<div class="details">
								<h5>Divisional Headquarters:<br>
								<a href="https://salvationarmyflorida.org" target=""><span>Website</span></a></h5>
							</div>

							<p>
								Divisional Communications Director&nbsp;<br>
								813.383.5668
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="col col-md-6">
			<div class="content">
				
				

			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<p>
	&nbsp;
</p>

<p>
	<style type="text/css">
.contacts
{
    margin: 0px auto 0px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px,1fr));
    grid-gap: 20px;
}
.contacts .card
{
    position: relative;
    width:350px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background:#f1f1f1;
    padding: 20px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 5px 5px 15px 0px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
    overflow: hidden;
    border:solid 2px #f0f0f0;
}
.contacts .card .layer
{
    position: absolute;
    top:calc(100% - 2px);
    left:0;
    width:100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(#f1f1f1, #fff);
    z-index: 1;
    transition: 0.5s;
}
.contacts .card:hover .layer
{
   top: 0;
}
.contacts .card .content
{
   position: relative;
   z-index: 2;
}
.contacts .card .content p
{
   font-size: 18px;
   line-height: 24px;
   color:#333;
}
.contacts .card .content .image
{
   width: 100px;
   height: 100px;
   margin: 0 auto;
   border-radius: 50%;
   overflow: hidden;
   border: 4px solid #fff;
   box-shadow: 5px 5px 15px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0);
}
.contacts .card .content .details h2
{ 
   font-size: 18px;
   color: #333;
}
.contacts .card .content .details h2 span
{
    color: #333;
    font-size: 14px;
    transition: 0.5s;
}
.contacts .card:hover .content .details h2 span
{
    color: red;
}
#ministriesGrid-icon .icon {
color: #fff !important;
}	</style>
</p>

